    "SuperGLUE has designated CommitmentBank as the assessment standard for the English RTE task, categorizing the veracity between the initial dataset pairs as \"Entailment,\" \"Neutral,\" and \"Contradiction.\"",
    "• MedNLI (Romanov and Shivade, 2018).",
    "The MedNLI dataset comprises RTE task data within the medical domain, annotated by expert physicians.",
    "During its development, transfer learning is applied, leveraging pre-existing open-source NLI datasets.",
    "Additionally, domain knowledge from external medical data and specialized medical terminology is integrated."
